Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.69,0:02:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.98,0:02:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Once there was a man who had it all,\NPirate King Gold Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.95,0:03:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,His final words spurred people\Nto take to the seas in droves:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.20,0:03:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,My treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.62,0:03:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.33,0:03:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.00,0:03:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ve left everything\Nthis world’s got to offer {\i1}there!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.30,0:03:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And so men set sail for the Grand Line\Nin pursuit of their dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.43,0:03:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, the world is in the midst\Nof the Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.45,0:03:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it a quiet night?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.32,0:03:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm on watch, but it's \Nbeen calm all night long.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.03,0:03:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no need to man the helm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.66,0:03:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm working myself to the bone for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.32,0:03:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind that I'm all bones!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.67,0:03:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.81,0:03:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Laboon...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.87,0:03:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You know Luffy-san and his buddies?\NI've joined their crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.41,0:04:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,They are great people.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.02,0:04:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But they are more than just that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.09,0:04:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I found something incredible\Nearlier this afternoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.84,0:04:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It told of Luffy-san and his crew's fearsome\Nadventures and their battle-filled days.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.55,0:04:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I have joined them,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.46,0:04:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I must prove that I am worthy\Nto call myself a crewmate!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.06,0:04:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't you agree, Laboon?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.60,0:04:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.97,0:04:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll wake you up with a song.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.05,0:04:43.22,Shanty ♪,,0,0,0,,White handkerchief,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.05,0:04:43.22,Alt,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.22,0:04:44.97,Shanty ♪,,0,0,0,,don't let him find you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.22,0:04:44.97,Alt,,0,0,0,,The sun hasn't risen yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.97,0:04:47.60,Shanty ♪,,0,0,0,,Run for it
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.97,0:04:47.60,Alt,,0,0,0,,Let me catch some more Z's!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.60,0:04:51.31,Shanty ♪,,0,0,0,,White handkerchief...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.60,0:04:51.31,Alt,,0,0,0,,Forget Brook. Someone make Luffy stop snoring!
