Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.51,0:05:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the plan, Navigator?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.95,0:05:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If we use the paddle, we could keep\Nmoving through these calm waters.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.39,0:05:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Based on the weather,\Nthis lull should only last today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.15,0:05:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we don't need to use our precious cola.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.34,0:05:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This is good!\NSanji, your cooking really is the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.68,0:05:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Robin-chan, have a second\Nhelping of the seafood salad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.09,0:05:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.88,0:05:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What's gotten into you, Brook?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.50,0:05:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Why have you been so hyper all morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.87,0:05:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something exciting happen, Brook?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.28,0:05:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He said that he saw our ship's log\Nwhile he was on watch yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.07,0:05:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! I just so happened\Nto read a small portion of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.59,0:05:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, it left me astonished!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.13,0:05:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't been able to \Nsettle down ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.63,0:05:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The incident at Thriller Bark was\Nonly the tip of the iceberg for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.63,0:05:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You stopped a civil war in\Nthe desert kingdom, Alabasta.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.73,0:06:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You had a grand adventure\Non the legendary sky island!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.45,0:06:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, you took on \Nthe World Government in a
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.15,0:06:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,massive fight at Water Seven!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.97,0:06:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so surprised, I \Nnearly had a heart attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.52,0:06:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, but I don't have a heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.27,0:06:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I wonder what sort of stories\Nwill get added to the log.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.62,0:06:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Brook, your name is going to\Nstart appearing in it now, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.49,0:06:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,About that! Now that I am your crewmate,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.73,0:06:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,it is imperative that I make myself useful!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.40,0:06:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I get why you're eager to work hard,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.29,0:06:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,\Nbut first let me give you a word of advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.50,0:06:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd love to hear it, Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.04,0:06:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,With this crew, never let your\Nguard down during a meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.18,0:06:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it! I, Quick Draw Brook, shall be
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.56,0:06:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,\Nready for the enemy to strike at any time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.88,0:06:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently we didn't warn you soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.94,0:06:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I claim those noodles!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.17,0:06:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Please wait a second! Luffy-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.10,0:07:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,They're good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.26,0:07:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I should not have let my guard down,\Neven for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.48,0:07:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well! I shall work \Nmyself to the bone to become
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.84,0:07:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,a true pal as soon as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.98,0:07:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm already nothing but bones...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.08,0:07:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanji-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.70,0:07:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate it. Since \Nyou're washing the dishes,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.89,0:07:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I can take my time with Nami-san's tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.82,0:07:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,As your pal, I am dying to help\Neveryone in extravagant ways,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.23,0:07:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'll do anything to make\Nmyself useful for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.59,0:07:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a great attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.36,0:07:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I'm a skeleton, I should work\Ntill I'm bone tired on the small stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.55,0:07:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm going to give Nami-san her tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.27,0:07:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Sanji-san, where do these go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.71,0:07:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, over in the...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.52,0:07:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't drop them, even if it kills you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.48,0:07:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm already dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.58,0:08:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,--And "kaboom!"\N--Don't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.22,0:08:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.69,0:08:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Splendid!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.56,0:08:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.30,0:08:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't trust you to do the dishes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.19,0:08:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, then I'll take this \Ntea to Nami-san instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.50,0:08:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Wait! I was gonna take it to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.38,0:08:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami-san, I've brought you some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.08,0:08:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.86,0:08:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,May I see your panties?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.95,0:08:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,--Bam!\N--That came out of nowhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.55,0:08:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a nautical chart?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.25,0:08:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been pretty busy lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.88,0:08:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a great chance to work on it,\Nsince the ship isn't going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.93,0:08:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it your dream to \Ndraw a map of the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.90,0:08:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. I want to navigate\Nacross the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.00,0:08:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and make a world map based on what I've seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.51,0:08:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.80,0:09:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If there is anything\NI could do to help, please let me know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.56,0:09:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, would you like another cup?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.76,0:09:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.16,0:09:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That sentiment is enough for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.38,0:09:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You are both beautiful and humble!\NNami-san, you truly are wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.17,0:09:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Really! I'm not that great.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.27,0:09:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you truly are--ouch! Hot! Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.97,0:09:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.47,0:09:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,My, I nearly burned my fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.80,0:09:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that I have any skin to burn!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.22,0:09:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,My map!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.22,0:09:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What have I done?!\NThat was horribly careless of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.22,0:09:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.78,0:09:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! I wiped it clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.89,0:09:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you wiped it clean of everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.56,0:09:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what I wanted!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.80,0:09:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be taking my leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.93,0:09:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I get the feeling that I won't be\Nthe least bit useful if this keeps up...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.37,0:09:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.97,0:09:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.41,0:10:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,These two are about to do something neat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.83,0:10:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You should watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.75,0:10:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.38,0:10:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Chopper-san, what are you doing up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.36,0:10:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm drying these herbs in the sun,\Nsince the weather is so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.95,0:10:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, Franky is gonna test his new weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.82,0:10:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! This is the long-distance\N"Super Franky Cannon."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.76,0:10:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It runs on cola energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.53,0:10:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Its range is several times
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.10,0:10:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,that of a conventional cannon. \NPlus it's super accurate!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.73,0:10:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Combined with my sniper skills,\Nwe'll be totally unstoppable!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.38,0:10:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This is exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.18,0:10:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I have butterflies in my stomach!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.78,0:10:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.22,0:10:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me! Let me know if there\Nis anything I could do to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.69,0:10:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. In that case, please get\Nanother barrel of cola to play it safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.23,0:10:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a problem. It would be my pleasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.35,0:10:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This must be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.27,0:10:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the barrel of cola!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.94,0:11:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Great! Now if you could pour it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.50,0:11:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.77,0:11:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Target: That rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.71,0:11:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it! Locking on to the rock at 2 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.77,0:11:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,--Fire!\N--Firing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.72,0:11:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,--Huh?\N--That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.57,0:11:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Usopp, increase the pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.34,0:11:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, you've got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.86,0:11:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, this doesn't look good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.39,0:11:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.26,0:11:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This was a huge flop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.92,0:11:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It should have worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.68,0:11:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This is kinda salty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.02,0:11:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Something is mixed with the cola.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.41,0:11:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This is soy sauce.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.46,0:11:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.90,0:12:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Show a little remorse!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.40,0:12:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You mistook a soy sauce barrel\Nfor a cola barrel, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.45,0:12:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're right! This \Nwas a soy sauce barrel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.29,0:12:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannon believe I made that mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.74,0:12:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.08,0:12:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,--I'm terribly sorry!\N--Why did you grab a soy sauce barrel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.98,0:12:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,--I'm sorry!\N--This is no time for puns!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.98,0:12:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Brook, you're hilarious!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.92,0:12:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,--Don't give me any "I'm only bones" crap!\N--Now I'm all sticky!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.71,0:12:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, I have to wash all of\Nthe herbs I had set out to dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.71,0:12:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This meat tastes great\Nwith the soy sauce and cola!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.82,0:12:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you find a bright side to anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.50,0:12:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything I try ends up going horribly awry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.79,0:12:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, Zoro-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.28,0:12:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This is no time to watch in admiration!\NI'm a fellow swordsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.25,0:12:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this meditation?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.68,0:13:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You enter a state of nothingness\Nwhile making your mind and body one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.99,0:13:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall join you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.18,0:13:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, Zoro-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.00,0:13:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I am fully aware that it is improper to\Ntalk during meditation sessions, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.69,0:13:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.43,0:13:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,--Well, you see...\N--What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.74,0:13:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to use the restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.51,0:13:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't need to know that! Head on over--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.97,0:13:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,--The thing is...\N--What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.50,0:13:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,...my legs went numb, so I can't stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.73,0:13:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any muscles to go numb?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.76,0:13:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Zoro-san, I'm on the verge\Nof having an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.50,0:13:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,For real? W-Wait, hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.45,0:13:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,--I'm gonna leak! It's coming!\N--I'll take you! W-Wait! Hey, hold it in!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.79,0:13:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite what I want, I've \Nbeen nothing but a nuisance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.47,0:13:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,This is awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.93,0:13:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Robin-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.37,0:13:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.61,0:13:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anything I could \Ndo to be of assistance?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.58,0:13:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Not in particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.82,0:14:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.98,0:14:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Brook, why are you so anxious?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.19,0:14:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Anxious?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.62,0:14:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I get the feeling you're afraid\Nof something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.94,0:14:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I mistaken?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.16,0:14:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You are absolutely right, Robin-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.20,0:14:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. I am terribly \Nanxious and scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.27,0:14:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,When Luffy-san first asked me\Nto join his crew, I was thrilled!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.98,0:14:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Those simple words filled me with joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.41,0:14:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And then my heart danced
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.59,0:14:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,with excitement when I defeated \NOars alongside everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.59,0:14:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,May I join your crew?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.06,0:14:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.23,0:14:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.23,0:14:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But does he truly want me in his crew?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.33,0:14:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If we continue to head toward the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.37,0:14:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no doubt that powerful foes and\Ntrials beyond our imagination await us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.80,0:15:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid that I will be\Nboth useless and a hindrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.21,0:15:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And if that proves true, I
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.35,0:15:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,might get kicked off the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.04,0:15:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right... I'm afraid\Nof losing my friends again
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.56,0:15:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and returning to that\Npainfully long life of solitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.39,0:15:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.26,0:15:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,...also anxious for the longest of times.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.18,0:15:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.72,0:15:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,...also anxious for the longest of times.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.06,0:15:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I was constantly afraid that I\Nwas unworthy to be their friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.99,0:15:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That is why I believed I could\Nbecome worthy of them
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.06,0:15:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,by throwing away my life for their sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.39,0:16:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Robin-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.14,0:16:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how far I go on the sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.95,0:16:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a huge enemy that I can't shake off...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.32,0:16:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,...because the world and\Nits darkness are my enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.66,0:16:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I didn't want\Nyou to come to rescue me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.85,0:16:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm going to die someday anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.76,0:16:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to die right here, right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.40,0:16:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't realize that was how you felt...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.34,0:16:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But I was mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.12,0:16:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That isn't what it means to be a true friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.90,0:16:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Robin-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.21,0:16:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.04,0:16:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oomph!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.06,0:16:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Brook, we've got food! It's lunchtime.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.43,0:16:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.43,0:16:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanji worked extra hard to make\Na full-course seafood lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.20,0:16:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I just know it'll be good!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.17,0:16:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.91,0:16:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What's keeping you? Get a move on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.58,0:16:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you absolutely certain I'm welcome?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.55,0:17:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,\NThat I may join the Straw Hat Crew?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.51,0:17:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.84,0:17:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, give it some thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.74,0:17:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I decided to let you join,\Nso I'm glad to have you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.99,0:17:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Now forget about that. Let's eat! Food!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.39,0:17:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.20,0:18:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the Straw Hats have \Ncalm days like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.44,0:18:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Usopp, let's catch dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.35,0:18:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.25,0:18:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,How many years--no, decades--has it been
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.97,0:18:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,\Nsince I enjoyed such a carefree nap?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.53,0:19:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Brook! Are you gonna sleep forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.78,0:19:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up! We spotted an island!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.76,0:19:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a Summer Island! It has a beach!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.10,0:19:09.37,Alt,,0,0,0,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.11,0:19:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was wandering the ocean alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.94,0:19:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I would dream about my old\Nfriends and Laboon in my sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.62,0:19:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I would jump awake with happiness,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.37,0:19:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,only to face the painful reality\Nfilled with despair and solitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.48,0:19:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Sleep was by no means a peaceful escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.85,0:19:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I listen carefully now...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.72,0:19:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Robin, what do you \Nthink of these outfits?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.24,0:19:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I think you'd look \Ngood in this and this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.62,0:20:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.66,0:20:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.23,0:20:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,My pals are near me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.77,0:20:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Even dead and skeletonized...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.74,0:20:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'm truly glad to be alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.51,0:22:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a short break time
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.61,0:22:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,before the next adventure \Neventually falls upon us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.04,0:22:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, let your weary bones rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.77,0:22:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Laboon,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.33,0:22:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,it looks like I will have
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.49,0:22:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,a slew of stories to \Nshare when we meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.83,0:22:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you're looking forward to them!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.98,0:22:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The wind has picked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.36,0:23:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.28,0:23:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.34,0:23:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oomph!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.41,0:23:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about time we set out.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.29,0:23:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.89,0:23:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise to work my butt off!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.33,0:23:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm a skeleton, so I don't have a butt.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.63,0:23:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We've reached the Red Line at last!
